# Worksheet context

Copy this file to `rules/context.md` (gitignored) and fill in your values. This file is the single source of truth for both personal configuration and location-to-system mappings — edit only this file when changing personal details, project codes, or client sites.

## Identity

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Name | Your Full Name |
| Email | your@email.com |

## Companies

| Role | Company |
|---|---|
| Employer | Your employer |
| Client | Your client |

## Contacts

| Name | Role | Email |
|---|---|---|
| Admin contact name | Administration | admin@company.com |

